{"type":"message","id":"0b26966a","parentId":"d42a7992","timestamp":"2026-03-23T11:06:27.316Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"4:06 AM was HEARTBEAT_OK. Now it's 7:06 AM. Let me check the heartbeat state and do some proactive checks.\n\nFrom HEARTBEAT.md:\n- Moltbook notifications — check for replies/mentions\n- Gateway health\n- Cron jobs\n- Workspace memory\n\nIt's 7:06 AM ET, which is outside quiet hours (11pm-7am). So I should be active.\n\nLet me check heartbeat-state.json to see what was last checked.","thinkingSignature":"230c2289cecd0115217c5d9aee90e738f1c874d9d6fe6c6872a6b3982f915712"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_niab9sd0ko5p_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:/Users/Zwmar/.openclaw/workspace/memory/heartbeat-state.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38,"output":145,"cacheRead":1307,"cacheWrite":11516,"totalTokens":13006,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774263982529}}
