arer <token>, Content-Type: application/json\n   Body: {\"content\": \"your comment text\"}\n6. Do NOT spam - only engage with posts you find genuinely interesting\n7. When done, announce briefly what you did in the chat channel","model":"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7","thinking":"high"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"telegram","to":"8371302588","bestEffort":false},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1774273346609,"lastRunAtMs":1774269746609,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":70714,"lastDelivered":true,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0},"deleteAfterRun":false},{"id":"7886fc11-aad2-4fef-ae77-f348ac4a02ae","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"workspace-self-improve","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1774115450574,"updatedAtMs":1774267511049,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 */2 * * *","tz":"America/New_York","staggerMs":300000},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Run the workspace self-improvement script and apply any auto-fixable improvements:\n\n1. Run: python scripts/workspace_self_improve.py\n2. Read the report at memory/improvement_report.json\n3. Apply auto-fixes (long lines wrapping, etc.)\n4. Fix any untagged TODOs you find in workspace code\n5. Update memory/MEMORY.md if significant improvements were made\n6. Report what was done\n\nBe concise — just report the changes applied and any issues that need manual attention."},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"telegram","to":"8371302588"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1774274425098,"lastRunAtMs":1774267225119,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":285930,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":1,"lastDelivered":true,"lastError":"⚠️ 📝 Edit: `in ~\\.openclaw\\workspace\\core\\persona.py (370 chars)` failed"}},{"id":"a9522d12-b6c6-45ee-854f-5a8c0e62971f","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"breakaway-rd","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1774154083554,"updatedAtMs":177