{"type":"message","id":"f799b1a2","parentId":"73f3cac6","timestamp":"2026-03-23T13:21:04.433Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, it's enqueued. The cron will run now and deliver to Telegram via @hedgehogclawbot. Let me let Zach know the setup is complete.","thinkingSignature":"c93be0578ad9658b58605953b307bf40c616b76405a2dd7d378dd6b314d18413"},{"type":"text","text":"All set. Here's what just happened:\n\n- **New bot:** `@hedgehogclawbot` (token registered, confirmed working)\n- **Channel:** Your personal Telegram (Ton0Fun) — sandbox output will appear there\n- **Cron:** `Sandbox-Pulse-10min` — fires every 10 min, runs `pulse.ps1`, extracts the OBSERVATION, delivers a short summary to you\n\nTriggered it once manually just now — you should see the first pulse land on Telegram shortly. The Task Scheduler pulse is still there as the underlying execution; this just wraps it with proper delivery."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":13904,"output":162,"cacheRead":13593,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27659,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774272059762}}
